---
title: Cal Smart Apple and Double Salmon Salad with Cranberry Dressing
description: This elegant salad comes with the tastiest toppings – warm caramelized apples, feta cheese and zesty croutons. plus a delicious piece of pan-seared salmon to turn this oh-so-easy salad into a meal.

